  "name": "generic-generator-profiles",
  "notes": "All Standard, Flexible and Curtailable connections are categorised into Wind, Photovoltaic, Battery or Other dependant on their fuel type within the application. An annual half hourly profile is provided for each fuel type. \r\n\r\nPlease see the guidance document for further information.  \r\n\r\nhttps://dso.nationalgrid.co.uk/curtailment-analysis-data-usage-guidance\r\n\r\nTo reference between the bus numbers used in this data set and bus name used within the LTDS please see the [Bus Index](https://connecteddata.nationalgrid.co.uk/dataset/curtailment_buses)",
